* GF180MCU-D textbook-style differential cascode/transformer RF PA seed.
* Pins: gnda vdda rfin rfout vbias
* The single-ended RFPA testbench is adapted with ideal internal balun/combiner
* elements. This is runnable for schematic experiments, not transformer signoff.
.subckt {{netlist_name}} gnda vdda rfin rfout vbias

* Ideal single-ended to differential input drive around vbias.
CIN rfin rfin_ac {{ Cin_value }}
RINLEAK rfin_ac gnda 1G
EINP gatep vbias rfin_ac gnda 0.5
EINN gaten vbias rfin_ac gnda -0.5
RGP gatep vbias {{ Rgatebias_value }}
RGN gaten vbias {{ Rgatebias_value }}

* Internal cascode bias seed.
RVC1 vdda vcas {{ RvcasTop_value }}
RVC2 vcas gnda {{ RvcasBot_value }}
CVBYP vcas gnda 5p

* Differential common-source devices.
M1 midp gatep gnda gnda nfet_03v3.12 l={{ M1_L }}u w={{ M1_W }}u m={{ M1_M }}
M2 midn gaten gnda gnda nfet_03v3.12 l={{ M2_L }}u w={{ M2_W }}u m={{ M2_M }}

* Cascode devices for reverse isolation and voltage sharing.
MCAS1 drainp vcas midp gnda nfet_03v3.12 l={{ MCAS1_L }}u w={{ MCAS1_W }}u m={{ MCAS1_M }}
MCAS2 drainn vcas midn gnda nfet_03v3.12 l={{ MCAS2_L }}u w={{ MCAS2_W }}u m={{ MCAS2_M }}

* Idealized RF feed. Current is split across the differential halves.
IBP vdda drainp 4m
IBN vdda drainn 4m
RDP drainp gnda 1G
RDN drainn gnda 1G

* Optional neutralization seeds. Set Cneut_value small/nonzero in the config.
CNEUTP drainp gaten {{ Cneut_value }}
CNEUTN drainn gatep {{ Cneut_value }}

* Passive transformer/combiner seed. This is still idealized, but unlike an
* active VCVS combiner it does not create output power by itself.
RPRI_P drainp pri_p 2
LPRI pri_p pri_n 80n
RPRI_N pri_n drainn 2
RSEC rfout sec_t 2
LSEC sec_t gnda 80n
KOUT LPRI LSEC 0.85
ROUTLEAK rfout gnda 1G

.ends {{netlist_name}}
